          "en.tashayyu": [
            "1 – Ẓafar b. Ḥamdūn b. Shaddād, al-Bādirā’ī, Abū Manṣūr.  He narrated from Ibrāhīm al-Aḥmarī.  There was weakness in his madhhab."
